Ubuntu 20.04配置ip地址：
vim /etc/netplan/00-installer-config.yaml
i
dhcp4: no
dhcp6: no
addresses: [x.x.x.x/24]
gateway4: x.x.x.x
nameservers:
      addresses: [x.x.x.x,x.x.x.x]

Esc:wq!
netplan apply

apt install openssh-server
vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config
i
permitrootlogin yes
Strictmodes yes
Esc:wq!
service ssh restart

tar xvf xxx.tar.gz


初始设置root密码：
passwd root
password_for_current_user
password_for_root
retype_password_for_root

切换root用户
su root

查询网卡地址
ip add
